    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text> Artists who specialize in painting altarpieces, which are objects in a Christian church, usually framed and either set on the rear part of the altar or hung on the wall behind the altar.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
